articles.author: Sofia Cox, Irene Nasser, Kathleen Magramo
articles.title: ‘I’m just so grateful:’ Castaway and his dog who survived months adrift at sea back on dry land - CNN
articles.description: An Australian sailor who spent months adrift in the Pacific Ocean alongside his beloved dog has recounted his remarkable tale of surviving on raw fish and rainwater after finally making it safely back to dry land.
